SELECT 
       [PrcCode]
      ,[PrcName]
      ,[DimCode]
      ,[U_Owner]
      ,[U_PorfApp]
      ,[U_OwnerMail]
      ,[U_Secondary]
      ,[U_SecMail]
      ,[U_PorfApp2]
      ,[Active]
      ,T0.[ValidTo]
      ,T0.u_porf
       ,DB_NAME() [DB_NAME]
 FROM [dbo].OPRC  t0 inner join [dbo].OACT T1 on t0.PrcCode= t1.U_PORF_Dep OR T0.PrcCode=T1.U_PORF_Alloc
 
 where Active <> 'N' AND T1.U_PORF='Y'
 GROUP BY 
     [PrcCode]
      ,[PrcName]
      ,[DimCode]
      ,[U_Owner]
      ,[U_PorfApp]
      ,[U_OwnerMail]
      ,[U_Secondary]
      ,[U_SecMail]
      ,[U_PorfApp2]
      ,[Active]
      ,T0.[ValidTo]
      ,T0.u_porf

/****** Script for SelectTopNRows command from SSMS  ******/
SELECT [ID]
      ,[_Procedure]
      ,[_StartTime]
      ,[_EndTime]
      ,[_ExecutedBy]
      ,[_Parent]
      ,[_Comments]
      ,[_Result]
      ,[_FailReason]
      ,[_PCAppSoftwareVersion]
      ,[_Deleted]
      ,[_DeletedBy]
      ,[_DeletedTime]
      ,[_InsertTime]
      ,[_LastUpdateTime]
      ,[_OriginalProcedureId]
      ,[_QcApprovalTime]
      ,[_QcApprover]
      ,[_Device]
      ,[_DeviceSoftwareVersion]
  FROM [QcOo_reporting].[dbo].[_DeviceProcedureData]
  WHERE [_StartTime] >='20180101' and COALESCE ([_StartTime],getdate()) >= '@{activity('get watermark').output.firstRow.highValue}'

SELECT 
	ItemCode,
	ISNULL(FrgnName, ItemName) AS ItemName, 
	CardCode, 
	ItmsGrpCod, 
	U_ServiceItem,
	DB_NAME() AS [DB_NAME],
        U_PORF,
	cast ( LastPurPrc  as float) LastPurPrc   ,
	LastPurDat ,
	LastPurCur 
 FROM [dbo].[OITM]

WHERE frozenFor = 'N'
AND PrchseItem = 'Y'
AND U_PORF = 'Y'
